.Dd December 1, 2014
.Dt RUMP 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm librump
.Nd Rump kernel base
.Sh LIBRARY
rump kernel base (librump, \-lrump)
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In rump/rump.h
.In rump/rump_syscalls.h
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The base of a
.Xr rumpkernel 7
is provided by the
.Nm
library.
In addition to fundamental routines such as kernel memory allocators
and locking,
.Nm
provides system call wrappers.
.Pp
Like the
.Xr rumpuser 3
library,
.Nm
is a mandatory component and is present in every rump kernel.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr rumpuser 3 ,
.Xr rumpkernel 7
